Here's how to release Hailo:

# Get custom build tools:

    # With fixes to override MakeMaker.pm
    git clone git://github.com/avar/dist-zilla.git
    # With POD UTF-8 fixes
    git clone git://github.com/avar/dist-zilla-plugin-readmefrompod.git

# Build Hailo

    # Build Hailo, see Hailo-* for what'll be released
    perl -Iinc -I ~/g/dist-zilla/lib -I ~/g/dist-zilla-plugin-readmefrompod/lib $(which dzil) build
    # Test it
    perl -Iinc -I ~/g/dist-zilla/lib -I ~/g/dist-zilla-plugin-readmefrompod/lib $(which dzil) test
    # Now commit everything but dzil.ini and Changelog and:
    perl -Iinc -I ~/g/dist-zilla/lib -I ~/g/dist-zilla-plugin-readmefrompod/lib $(which dzil) release
